Potential Gains in Life Expectancy Associated With Achieving Treatment Goals in 
US Adults With Type 2 Diabetes.

Kianmehr H(1), Zhang P(2), Luo J(3), Guo J(1)(4), Pavkov ME(2), Bullard KM(2), 
Gregg EW(5), Ospina NS(6), Fonseca V(7), Shi L(8), Shao H(1)(2)(4).

