(1)Department of Pharmaceutical Outcomes and Policy, College of Pharmacy, 
University of Florida, Gainesville.
(2)Division of Diabetes Translation, Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, 
Atlanta, Georgia.
(3)Division of General Internal Medicine, University of Pittsburgh School of 
